text: Miloš Kratochvíl (born 26 April 1996) is a Czech footballer who plays for Jablonec as a midfielder. ==Career== ===FK Senica=== Kratochvíl made his professional debut for Senica against Slovan Bratislava on 17 July 2016.FK Senica - ŠK Slovan Bratislava 0:1 (0:0) 16.07.2016, futbalnet.sk ==References== ==External links== * Eurofotbal profile * * Futbalnet Profile * Profile at FAČR official site Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Czech footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC Zbrojovka Brno players Category:FC Viktoria Plzeň players Category:FK Baník Sokolov players Category:FK Senica players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Expatriate footballers in Slovakia Category:Czech expatriate sportspeople in Slovakia Category:FK Jablonec players
